# Boggle Game in Python

## Description
This project is a Python implementation of the classic Boggle word game.
The game generates a 4x4 grid of random letters, and players try to find as many words as possible by connecting adjacent letters within a time limit.

## Features
- Randomized 4x4 letter grid generation.
- Word validation against a standard English dictionary.
- Score calculation based on word length.
- User-friendly command-line interface.

## How to Play
1. Run the code on python IDE
2. Have fun
